      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALCOMBZ (1) is a three-year-old gelding by Majestic Son making his debut for Courtney Slater. Has been showing ability at the trials, finishing second to a subsequent winner in the latest hitout at Melton and winning here prior. The ace draw gives him the chance to kick off with a win. LOW LIE THE FIELDS (5) showed good improvement second-up, beaten less than 4m as runner up at this venue. Draws a couple of spots wider but should strip fitter again so may progress further. RIDETHELIGHTNING (4) did a good job for fourth in a decent line-up here last start. Could measure up here. CHAMPAGNE GEMMA (6) was checked and broke when resuming. Fitter so worth another chance. WATCH THE BAY (3) has had a series of second row draws so may do better from this barrier.",
